name: Moot
tagline: Moot is an online dynamic discussion board , brings in live experience of group discussion and debate.
body:
### Welcome to Moot.
I have this idea of coming up with a dynamic website ,holding all powers of a group discussion and debate,at the same time providing live experience and instant connectivity with other people taking part in these activites:

```
$ cd tuhinrawat/moot
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Authors and Contributors
Hi I am @tuhinrawat, looking for some more enthusiastic team members for my team,People with knowlede of jQuery,PHP and mysql are welcomed and anyone who is interested in my project are more welcomed .
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
